    "description": "Shoei Yakuhin Co.,Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in trading of chemicals, daily necessities, and civil engineering and construction materials in Japan and internationally. The company provides various oleo chemicals, such as fatty acids, aliphatic amines, aliphatic alcohols, and glycerin; and petrochemicals, synthetic resins, solvents and mineral oils, pigments, and anionic, nonionic, cationic, and amphoteric surfactants, as well as fragrance, and inorganic chemicals. It also offers daily necessities, including household detergents, industrial-grade cleaners, deodorizers, and cosmetics. Further, it offers civil engineering and construction materials, such as ground stabilization grouts; repairing and reinforcing concrete materials and additives; soil improving agents; and other products. The company was founded in 1937 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
